<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 14:04:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>基地组织俘虏了我。以色列必须采取什么措施才能释放哈马斯扣押的人质？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/al-qaeda-held-me-captive-what-must-israel-do-to-free-the-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018b-e692-d867-abab-f7b6581e0000</link><description>就像哈马斯将 10 月 7 日对以色列的袭击命名为阿克萨洪水行动一样，我的基地组织绑架者也将自己视为改变全球的灾难的一部分，而哈马斯人质面临的危险每时每刻都在加剧。这是我要告诉以色列决策者的话</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 13:58:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/al-qaeda-held-me-captive-what-must-israel-do-to-free-the-hostages-held-by-hamas/0000018b-e692-d867-abab-f7b6581e0000</guid></item><item><title>随着法国反犹太主义的高涨，一些犹太人采取新措施来隐藏他们的宗教信仰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/as-antisemitism-spikes-in-france-some-jews-adopt-new-measures-to-hide-their-religion/0000018b-e73c-d867-abab-f7bc1d100000</link><description>当法国犹太人试图通过移除门框上的门柱等方式保持低调时，社区领袖建议不要“让反犹太主义者觉得他们已经取得了一些成功”，一位大屠杀幸存者告诉巴黎的年轻犹太人：“你应该这样做”。不要害怕&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 13:54:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/as-antisemitism-spikes-in-france-some-jews-adopt-new-measures-to-hide-their-religion/0000018b-e73c-d867-abab-f7bc1d100000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸成为以色列战争中令人不安的第三条战线</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/the-west-bank-emerges-as-a-third-and-troubling-front-in-israels-war/0000018b-e764-df9a-ab8b-ffeccb7f0000</link><description>以色列可以继续打着“追捕哈马斯”的旗号镇压加沙，打着“打击恐怖主义”的口号推平约旦河西岸，但我们必须明白，每发生一次死亡，新一代巴勒斯坦年轻人就会加入到反对以色列的斗争中。</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 12:18:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/the-west-bank-emerges-as-a-third-and-troubling-front-in-israels-war/0000018b-e764-df9a-ab8b-ffeccb7f0000</guid></item><item><title>散居海外的犹太人成为以色列行为的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/diaspora-jews-are-hostages-to-israels-behavior/0000018b-e420-d867-abab-f5a4592d0000</link><description>散居海外的犹太人经历了惨痛的教训，无论他们的派别或政治立场如何，他们都会成为严厉批评以色列行为的出气筒，煽动行为会演变成反犹太主义。现在是以色列至少承认这一现实的时候了</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 08:32:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/.premium/diaspora-jews-are-hostages-to-israels-behavior/0000018b-e420-d867-abab-f5a4592d0000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔表示，以色列与哈马斯人质协议面临的挑战“只是后勤方面的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/negotiations-over-hostage-release-held-up-as-israel-waits-for-hamas/0000018b-e69d-dffa-adef-e69d32ea0000</link><description>卡塔尔总理阿勒萨尼表示，达成协议之前的剩余挑战“只是实际和后勤方面的挑战”。几小时前，《华盛顿邮报》报道称，双方已达成一项临时协议，以释放数十名妇女和儿童，以换取暂停五天的战斗。到达</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 08:32:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/negotiations-over-hostage-release-held-up-as-israel-waits-for-hamas/0000018b-e69d-dffa-adef-e69d32ea0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布了另外三名阵亡士兵的名字；卡塔尔称人质交易取得进展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-live/biden-says-gaza-and-west-bank-should-be-ruled-by-renewed-pa/0000018b-e568-dffa-adef-e76822250000</link><description>以色列国防军在周六宣布 8 人死亡后又公布了三名阵亡士兵的名字 ■ 以色列安全内阁批准燃料进入加沙 ■ 也门胡塞武装称他们将瞄准所有以色列拥有和运营的船只 ■ 以色列国防军称已拦截以色列北部的空中目标 ■卡塔尔总理表示，人质协议面临的挑战“非常小” ■ 《华盛顿邮报》报道，人质协议已接近达成协议 ■ 加沙医学界消息人士：以色列国防军在加沙南部汗尤尼斯发动袭击，死亡人数上升至 64 人 ■ 至少 1,200 名平民和士兵死亡自 10 月 7 日起； 236 名人质在加沙被扣押 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：12,300 人死亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 04:01:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article-live/biden-says-gaza-and-west-bank-should-be-ruled-by-renewed-pa/0000018b-e568-dffa-adef-e76822250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和世界必须认清反犹太主义者的本质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-world-must-recognize-antisemites-for-what-they-are/0000018b-e3be-d867-abab-f7be96930000</link><description>让我们考虑一下在自诩为人文自由主义者中变得如此流行的口号：从河流到海洋，巴勒斯坦将是自由的。实际上免费什么？</description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israel-and-the-world-must-recognize-antisemites-for-what-they-are/0000018b-e3be-d867-abab-f7be96930000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-e4e9-dffa-adef-e6e955bf0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:11:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-e4e9-dffa-adef-e6e955bf0000</guid></item><item><title>不合时宜：人质交易缺乏紧迫性已达到临界点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/out-of-time-the-lack-of-urgency-for-a-hostage-deal-is-reaching-a-tipping-point/0000018b-e416-dffa-adef-e61656e50000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 19 Nov 2023 00:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-19/ty-article-opinion/out-of-time-the-lack-of-urgency-for-a-hostage-deal-is-reaching-a-tipping-point/0000018b-e416-dffa-adef-e61656e50000</guid></item><item><title>随着以色列国防军进一步深入加沙，内塔尼亚胡的战时内阁在与哈马斯的人质协议上出现分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-split-over-terms-of-hostage-deal-as-idf-expands-operation/0000018b-e40e-d867-abab-f5ae6e680000</link><description>三个因素将决定战争的成败：释放人质、摧毁地道和消灭哈马斯高级指挥官。另一方坚持认为军方必须继续全力向哈马斯施加压力</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 23:47:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-split-over-terms-of-hostage-deal-as-idf-expands-operation/0000018b-e40e-d867-abab-f5ae6e680000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队公布在加沙战斗中丧生的 11 名士兵姓名</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-names-of-five-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-e480-d867-abab-f5a46bfc0000</link><description>随着以色列国防军深化地面行动，士兵在加沙地带北部被杀</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 23:01:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/israeli-army-releases-names-of-five-soldiers-killed-in-gaza-fighting/0000018b-e480-d867-abab-f5a46bfc0000</guid></item><item><title>罗杰·沃特斯：停止否认 10 月 7 日哈马斯暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/an-open-letter-to-roger-waters/0000018b-e3be-d168-a3ef-f7fe96410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 22:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/an-open-letter-to-roger-waters/0000018b-e3be-d168-a3ef-f7fe96410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队将一名在约旦河西岸清真寺投掷眩晕手榴弹的士兵停职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-soldier-seen-throwing-stun-grenade-at-west-bank-mosque/0000018b-e450-df9a-ab8b-fed84d250000</link><description>该事件发生之际，美国政府敦促以色列打击约旦河西岸的极端主义活动。 ■ 以色列国防军发言人：“这是一起违反以色列国防军价值观的严重事件”</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 22:13:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-19/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-suspends-soldier-seen-throwing-stun-grenade-at-west-bank-mosque/0000018b-e450-df9a-ab8b-fed84d250000</guid></item><item><title>拜登表示，美国准备对袭击约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的以色列“极端分子”实施签证禁令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/u-s-to-issue-visa-bans-on-israeli-extremists-attacking-palestinians-in-west-bank/0000018b-e409-df9a-ab8b-fec973190000</link><description>拜登总统在《华盛顿邮报》专栏文章中透露，此举是其政府自上台以来对以色列采取的最重大的惩罚措施</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 20:37:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/u-s-to-issue-visa-bans-on-israeli-extremists-attacking-palestinians-in-west-bank/0000018b-e409-df9a-ab8b-fec973190000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部阿拉伯城市25岁男子被枪杀，警方逮捕嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/25-year-old-shot-dead-in-northern-israeli-arab-city-police-arrest-suspect/0000018b-e3fa-d867-abab-f7fec22a0000</link><description>此次枪击事件使年初以来以色列阿拉伯社会的谋杀案数量达到210起，标志着自与哈马斯开战以来以色列阿拉伯人的谋杀案数量大幅减少</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 20:01:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/25-year-old-shot-dead-in-northern-israeli-arab-city-police-arrest-suspect/0000018b-e3fa-d867-abab-f7fec22a0000</guid></item><item><title>惊慌失措的人们离开希法医院，据报道加沙北部学校有数十人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/panicked-people-leave-shifa-hospital-while-dozens-reportedly-killed-at-north-gaza-school/0000018b-e3d5-df9a-ab8b-ffdd46250000</link><description>撤离后只剩下以色列军队和骨干人员来照顾那些病重而无法移动的人。以色列表示，加沙北部的医院是其旨在镇压哈马斯的地面攻势的主要目标，声称这些医院被用作激进分子的指挥中心和武器库</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 19:56:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/panicked-people-leave-shifa-hospital-while-dozens-reportedly-killed-at-north-gaza-school/0000018b-e3d5-df9a-ab8b-ffdd46250000</guid></item><item><title>以色列反对派领导人拉皮德试图争取利库德集团成员的支持以推翻内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-trying-to-muster-support-from-likud-mks-to-topple-netanyahu/0000018b-e391-dffa-adef-e791daee0000</link><description>Yesh Atid 主席 Yair Lapid 希望在不信任投票中获得足够的支持，并与利库德集团等议员进行了交谈。然而，许多MKs可能会拒绝依赖阿拉伯政党，而他的反对党伙伴本尼·甘茨(Benny Gantz)在选举民意调查中有支持，他更愿意提前举行选举</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 19:14:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/opposition-leader-lapid-trying-to-muster-support-from-likud-mks-to-topple-netanyahu/0000018b-e391-dffa-adef-e791daee0000</guid></item><item><title>人质家属游行抵达耶路撒冷，在内塔尼亚胡总理办公室前集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-march-reaches-jerusalem-rally-in-front-of-pm-netanyahus-office/0000018b-e326-d867-abab-f7a628140000</link><description>大约一万名游行者进入首都，随后将在特拉维夫举行另一场集会。这些家人稍后将会见以色列战时内阁的三名成员，而总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡尚未接受他们的邀请</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 16:31:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/hostages-families-march-reaches-jerusalem-rally-in-front-of-pm-netanyahus-office/0000018b-e326-d867-abab-f7a628140000</guid></item><item><title>以色列安全机构：哈马斯可能事先不了解新星节</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-establishment-hamas-likely-didnt-have-prior-knowledge-of-nova-festival/0000018b-e2ee-d168-a3ef-f7fe8ca20000</link><description>以色列高级安全官员估计，哈马斯通过无人机或降落伞飞行者发现了诺瓦音乐节，并利用其通信系统将恐怖分子引导至该地点</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:49:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/israeli-security-establishment-hamas-likely-didnt-have-prior-knowledge-of-nova-festival/0000018b-e2ee-d168-a3ef-f7fe8ca20000</guid></item><item><title>数百名布兰代斯校友威胁要停止捐款，除非亲巴勒斯坦组织恢复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-alumni-threaten-to-stop-donations-unless-pro-palestinian-group-reinstated/0000018b-e2f0-df9a-ab8b-fef86a7a0000</link><description>在写给布兰代斯大学校长的一封信中，校友们表示，除非学校收回有效禁止巴勒斯坦正义学生组织在校园内举办活动的决定，否则他们将撤回资助。</description><pubDate>Sat, 18 Nov 2023 15:24:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-18/ty-article/.premium/brandeis-alumni-threaten-to-stop-donations-unless-pro-palestinian-group-reinstated/0000018b-e2f0-df9a-ab8b-fef86a7a0000</guid></item></channel></rss>